OL,3,CMothers of disabled sons campaign for
OL,4,Ccameras in all care homes
OL,6,FTwo mothers are campaigning for a
OL,7,Fchange in the law after secret cameras
OL,8,Fthey installed in their disabled sons'
OL,9,Fcare homes uncovered neglect and poor
OL,10,Fcare.
OL,12,FLindsay Foskett and Sylvia Siddique
OL,13,Fwant cameras to be mandatory in all
OL,14,Fcare settings after they came forward
OL,15,Fto ITV News with their footage.
OL,17,FThey have met with the Liberal
OL,18,FDemocrat leader Ed Davey, who is
OL,19,Fpledging support for their campaign
OL,20,Fand to push it through Parliament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
