OL,3,CMothers of disabled sons campaign for
OL,4,Ccameras in all care homes
OL,6,FLindsay's son Connor and Sylvia's son
OL,7,FMikey are both disabled adults.
OL,9,FConnor has a rare genetic condition,
OL,10,Flearning disabilities and is autistic
OL,11,Fand Mikey is blind, autistic and has
OL,12,Flearning disabilities. Connor needs
OL,13,Fround-the-clock care, and Mikey has a
OL,14,Fcarer with him at all times throughout
OL,15,Fthe day, as well as being checked
OL,16,Fevery two hours in the night.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
