OL,3,CMothers of disabled sons campaign for
OL,4,Ccameras in all care homes
OL,6,F"What I witnessed when I installed
OL,7,Fthose CCTV cameras was horrific,"
OL,8,FSylvia told ITV News.
OL,10,FConnor and Mikey are not able to fully
OL,11,Fcommunicate with their families, and
OL,12,Fboth Lindsay and Sylvia say without
OL,13,Fthe cameras, they would never have
OL,14,Fknown about their sons' treatment.
OL,16,F"If it wasn't for myself fitting CCTV
OL,17,Fcameras in his flat, I think he would
OL,18,Fprobably not be here." said Sylvia.
OL,20,F"I never would have known," adds
OL,21,FLindsay.
