OL,6,F"I did have an inkling something was
OL,7,Fwrong with him. He was in a previous
OL,8,Fprovider where he had bruises on him
OL,9,Fand he couldn't tell me where they
OL,10,Fwere from. I think it's imperative
OL,11,Fthat we make cameras legal" said
OL,12,FLindsay.
OL,14,F"Something definitely needs to be
OL,15,Fdone. These people, they are way too
OL,16,Fvulnerable to just be left like this.
OL,17,FOnce those doors are closed...They
OL,18,Fcan't speak for themselves," Sylvia
OL,19,Fadded.
