OL,6,FSir Ed Davey MP's 17-year-old son John
OL,7,Falso has complex needs and receives
OL,8,Faround the clock care at home. The
OL,9,FLiberal Democrat leader agreed to back
OL,10,FLindsay and Sylvia's campaign in
OL,11,FParliament.
OL,13,F"I think your campaign is so
OL,14,Frelevant... Every parent in a way
OL,15,Ffeels this because they know that no
OL,16,Fone else is going to love and hold
OL,17,Ftheir child like they do."
