OL,6,F"One day I won't be here, my wife
OL,7,Fwon't be here, and he may well be in a
OL,8,Fcare home. He can't really communicate
OL,9,Fvery well."
OL,11,F"I think it is beyond time to act," he
OL,12,Ftold Lindsay and Sylvia.
OL,14,F"It's important we have a proper
OL,15,Fdebate to make sure we get it right,"
OL,16,Fsaid Ed Davey.
OL,18,F"Action has to be taken, that's going
OL,19,Fto require a change in the law.
