OL,6,F"The liberal argument is clear, it's
OL,7,Fprotecting them because they aren't
OL,8,Fable to protect themselves."
OL,10,FCameras are currently only used in
OL,11,Fcare settings on a case by case basis.
OL,13,FUnions and human rights groups are
OL,14,Flikely to oppose any blanket
OL,15,Finstallment of CCTV in all settings.
OL,17,FCritics say it could infringe the
OL,18,Frights of those being recorded.
