OL,6,F"Very often, blanket approaches won't
OL,7,Fbe respectful of people's human
OL,8,Frights...We have to think about
OL,9,Fpeople's rights to privacy, so the
OL,10,Fextent to which the people themselves
OL,11,Fcan consent (to cameras in their
OL,12,Fhome)."
OL,14,FMs Hosali also questioned if cameras
OL,15,Fwould actually address the issues at
OL,16,Fthe root of poor care, neglect and
OL,17,Fabuse.
