OL,3,CMothers of disabled sons campaign for
OL,4,Ccameras in all care homes
OL,6,F"If CCTV cameras are the answer, we're
OL,7,Fprobably asking the wrong question.
OL,8,FAnd I think that's the nub of the
OL,9,Fissue here, is that we're talking
OL,10,Fabout protecting people from inhumane,
OL,11,Fintegrating treatment. A CCTV camera
OL,12,Fmight help with that.
OL,14,F"But the bigger issue is why are they
OL,15,Fbeing subjected to inhumane and
OL,16,Fdegrading treatment? And we actually
OL,17,Fneed to address that culture of care
OL,18,Ffirst."
