OL,6,FEd Davey says that cameras must be
OL,7,Fpart of wider reform within the care
OL,8,Fsector, including a register for
OL,9,Fprofessionals working in the industry,
OL,10,Fin line with the General Medical
OL,11,FCouncil for doctors and the Nursing
OL,12,Fand Midwifery Council.
OL,14,FLindsay's petition has reached more
OL,15,Fthan 40,000 signatures, and the
OL,16,Fmothers have requested a meeting with
OL,17,Fthe government.
